show.description: The Last Recipe follows Aryan, a talented yet underestimated cook, as he battles personal struggles and a fierce culinary competition to save Zaika, a restaurant tied to his past. Amidst sabotage, betrayal, and a rekindled romance with Naina, Aryan’s journey culminates in a dramatic showdown proving his mastery and integrity.
